==Description==
The '''Brown Shard''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]] first encountered in [[Galar]].

==Details==
The Brown Shard can be used with [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}} to obtain items from [[Shard Trader|Shard Traders]].

==Mine Layout==
The Brown Shard appears in the Underground as a 4x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:BrownShardMine.png|100px]]

==Trades==
Brown Shards can be used in combination with other [[Shards]] to purchase the following items:
